Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.26,0:01:09.99,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, did you hear about class D?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.99,0:01:13.01,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About the test?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.01,0:01:15.51,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Sadako Notes right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.24,0:01:18.49,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, the Sadako Notes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.49,0:01:21.10,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap, I sort of want them too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.10,0:01:22.45,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.17,0:01:26.94,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kurumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.17,0:01:33.55,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, did I keep you waiting?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.55,0:01:35.96,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.96,0:01:38.14,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.14,0:01:40.66,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.04,0:01:45.67,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There've been lots of rumors about Sadako lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.67,0:01:48.42,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Especially since what happened last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.42,0:01:51.10,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's she really like anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.10,0:01:52.38,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.38,0:01:55.76,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I remember seeing her with Kazehaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.76,0:01:57.85,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.85,0:02:01.49,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if they're going out? Just kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.49,0:02:03.77,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.77,0:02:05.27,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.21,0:02:10.47,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can imagine him liking her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.61,0:02:15.64,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way, no way!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.64,0:02:19.41,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know what he's like, he can't help but be nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.41,0:02:22.53,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If anything it would be you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.45,0:02:24.97,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.97,0:02:27.86,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why not? You two are so close.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.86,0:02:30.37,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just because we were in the same middle school.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.37,0:02:32.66,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should just go out with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.66,0:02:34.05,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.05,0:02:37.51,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You might not like him, but he might start liking you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.51,0:02:40.14,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Lately,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.14,0:02:47.68,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,some strange things have been happening around me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.68,0:02:49.60,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Sadako.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.60,0:02:52.88,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, come on, make a funny face.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.88,0:02:55.41,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Funny face?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.41,0:02:56.12,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.12,0:02:57.36,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.03,0:03:00.95,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.41,0:03:09.68,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.68,0:03:11.17,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Darn.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.00,0:03:17.22,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so surprised and I can't explain it,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.22,0:03:20.79,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,but I'm happy that I'm not being avoided.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.79,0:03:22.26,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.26,0:03:25.72,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're saying good things happen when you laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.72,0:03:27.31,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Good things?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.31,0:03:30.32,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one's ever said that about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.20,0:03:32.46,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.46,0:03:35.63,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.63,0:03:36.77,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.77,0:03:38.44,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say something funny to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.44,0:03:42.07,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pops yelled at me for drinking pop!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.20,0:03:48.75,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was a failure.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.75,0:03:50.54,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In more ways than one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.54,0:03:54.42,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you look like that when you smile?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.42,0:03:54.88,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.88,0:03:55.65,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.65,0:03:56.99,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.99,0:03:59.96,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Yano-san, Yoshida-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.96,0:04:05.41,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're totally friends with Hirano-chan and Endou-chan now, Sadako.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.10,0:04:07.47,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,F-Frie—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.47,0:04:08.55,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.55,0:04:10.06,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.06,0:04:13.66,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,By the time we noticed...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.66,0:04:16.56,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.56,0:04:18.94,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the best time of my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.94,0:04:22.70,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, can I call you by your first name?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.70,0:04:24.52,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your last names are long.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.52,0:04:25.55,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.55,0:04:26.83,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Call me Ekko.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.83,0:04:28.28,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Tomo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.28,0:04:31.67,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can call us Chizu or Yano-chin or Ayane or whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.67,0:04:32.76,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.76,0:04:35.11,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chizu-chan and Ayane-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.11,0:04:37.25,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for filling in for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.25,0:04:40.06,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was smooth.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.06,0:04:40.82,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.82,0:04:41.84,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.84,0:04:45.53,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how you start calling each other by your first names.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.53,0:04:47.48,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I learned something new.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.48,0:04:49.98,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't smooth.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.98,0:04:53.87,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usually it just sort of happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.31,0:04:56.60,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you even know?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.60,0:04:58.06,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ekko.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.06,0:04:59.19,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.19,0:05:00.07,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chizu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.07,0:05:01.50,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayane.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.50,0:05:03.30,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're talking to you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.22,0:05:05.57,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.57,0:05:07.27,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.27,0:05:08.78,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Try it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.74,0:05:15.66,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayane-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.66,0:05:17.88,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.88,0:05:20.51,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C-C-C-C-Chizu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.51,0:05:22.14,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a lot of "Ahs" and "Chis."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.14,0:05:24.44,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,E-E-Ekko-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.44,0:05:26.22,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-T-Tomo-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.22,0:05:28.05,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's fresh!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.05,0:05:29.86,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sort of happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.39,0:05:42.51,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,They're happy for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.06,0:05:50.72,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're stiff enough as it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.72,0:05:53.83,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you start calling the girls by their first name?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.83,0:05:55.36,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By their first names?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.36,0:05:57.25,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that rude?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.25,0:05:59.11,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.11,0:06:02.50,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're really awkward, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.50,0:06:04.89,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it'll take a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.89,0:06:06.53,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Start with your close friends, maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.75,0:06:12.11,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here comes a good practice target.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.11,0:06:13.74,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Practice target?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.53,0:06:15.48,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.84,0:06:18.23,KimiTodo-Overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,Try calling him by his first name.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.23,0:06:21.73,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Y-Y-Yano-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.73,0:06:22.69,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.69,0:06:25.19,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-A-A-Ayane-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.19,0:06:27.65,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.65,0:06:31.56,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think you can fit in with everyone like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.56,0:06:33.41,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano-chin's so sadistic.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.41,0:06:36.06,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't you going to try harder?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.91,0:06:38.19,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.19,0:06:39.29,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kazehaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.29,0:06:41.88,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sadako's...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.01,0:06:50.91,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazehaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.91,0:06:51.97,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,That's his last name.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.86,0:06:56.81,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.58,0:07:02.68,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.68,0:07:03.77,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.77,0:07:06.95,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See, I told you, it's too hard on guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.95,0:07:09.26,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I said to start with the girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.26,0:07:11.11,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah right...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.39,0:07:16.16,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.16,0:07:18.68,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, start with the girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.68,0:07:19.34,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.34,0:07:20.54,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.54,0:07:23.86,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll talk to the guys like normal for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.09,0:07:29.20,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you made her do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.20,0:07:30.49,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.07,0:07:35.58,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,He talks nicely to everyone, regardless of gender,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.58,0:07:38.95,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,like Yano-san and Yoshida-san do for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.38,0:07:41.93,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kuronuma going "Kazehaya," huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.93,0:07:45.39,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazehaya-kun's a guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.39,0:07:47.38,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was wondering what you were going to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.34,0:07:51.72,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,He's different from Yano-san and Yoshida-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.44,0:07:55.56,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,He's really...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.03,0:07:59.12,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,a guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.35,0:08:06.46,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're choosing the sports day committee today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.46,0:08:09.35,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too much work. The P.E. committee can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.35,0:08:10.63,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, done.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.63,0:08:12.02,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.86,0:08:15.93,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazehaya, you're screwed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.81,0:08:16.91,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,He didn't even let anyone volunteer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.76,0:08:22.42,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, I'm also the committee representative.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.42,0:08:25.41,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You better show up, or I'll tell everyone about your embarrassing—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.39,0:08:25.41,KimiTodo-Overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.41,0:08:27.56,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get it, I'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.56,0:08:28.49,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.49,0:08:30.96,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You kids better win.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.96,0:08:35.20,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're kind of short on people, so if you end up competing in more than one sport you need to be athletic.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.20,0:08:38.08,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you've been in an event before, you need to be in it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.08,0:08:39.96,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're slow, you better not come.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.96,0:08:42.06,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're excused from school.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.69,0:08:44.83,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Asshole.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.83,0:08:47.12,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,And so...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.88,0:08:55.15,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can barely control myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.11,0:08:58.24,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm bursting with excitement!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.24,0:09:00.78,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the twice-a-year festival in my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.76,0:09:04.03,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the spirit!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.03,0:09:05.42,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For victory!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.52,0:09:07.17,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For victory!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.17,0:09:09.24,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beat them all!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.24,0:09:10.59,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.32,0:09:14.87,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I better not drag them down.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.87,0:09:16.82,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kuronuma, can you play soccer?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.18,0:09:19.36,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.25,0:09:21.04,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.04,0:09:24.27,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You look pretty slow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.27,0:09:26.39,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.39,0:09:27.96,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't bother.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.96,0:09:30.13,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can take the day off.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.03,0:09:38.48,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we practice during lunch then?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.48,0:09:39.50,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.50,0:09:40.68,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.05,0:09:44.93,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That'd help.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.53,0:09:48.68,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll do our best.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.89,0:09:53.27,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.72,0:09:58.05,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Practice for sports day, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.05,0:10:02.62,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't feel like it, but it'll probably be fun with Kazehaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.62,0:10:06.68,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazehaya didn't even have a chance to say no before he got chosen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.68,0:10:07.77,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.31,0:10:26.08,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have homeroom next, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.08,0:10:27.74,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.74,0:10:30.45,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if we're going to choose sports day events.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.45,0:10:35.23,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, Kazehaya's going to be the committee member representing class D.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.23,0:10:36.79,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.79,0:10:39.62,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should join.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.62,0:10:42.05,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.05,0:10:43.47,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it'll be good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.47,0:10:45.16,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.16,0:10:48.13,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You might even end up going out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.13,0:10:49.39,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.39,0:10:51.83,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, that wouldn't happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.83,0:10:54.90,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind joining the committee though.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.90,0:10:56.34,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do it, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.34,0:10:58.94,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't volunteer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.94,0:11:00.80,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm too shy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.80,0:11:03.77,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll nominate you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.71,0:11:07.42,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's getting embarrassed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.93,0:11:11.06,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here it comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.03,0:11:12.83,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sadako.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.82,0:11:14.79,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.66,0:11:26.42,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.70,0:11:29.58,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought so.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.29,0:11:36.30,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess we can't throw you in at the deep end.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.30,0:11:39.67,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We should start you off with kicking first.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.67,0:11:42.34,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.34,0:11:45.77,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We all sort of expected it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.77,0:11:48.52,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She should just laugh it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.52,0:11:51.80,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She might even scare the opponents that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.80,0:11:55.09,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe she'll bring us good luck and we'll win.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.33,0:11:58.03,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chizu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.03,0:12:01.11,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We better head back, we're going to be late for fifth period.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.11,0:12:02.98,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.98,0:12:05.53,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lunch break is too short.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.53,0:12:09.40,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the clubs use the fields after school.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.71,0:12:14.15,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,It's only practice and I'm already dragging them down.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.15,0:12:17.38,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't use up their precious time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.38,0:12:19.72,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to practice alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.56,0:12:22.73,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need a ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.73,0:12:24.43,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to practice alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.50,0:12:26.35,KimiTodo-Overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you mumbling about? You're creepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.35,0:12:28.77,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's chanting something.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.77,0:12:30.39,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.02,0:12:32.81,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The guys are still playing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.31,0:12:37.34,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.34,0:12:39.09,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Kazehaya-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.22,0:12:41.51,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.51,0:12:44.07,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like he's chilling as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.64,0:12:46.84,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.42,0:12:49.80,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen him exercising.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.80,0:12:53.54,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what he looks like playing softball.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.54,0:12:55.76,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We better go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.76,0:12:58.29,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to be late for fifth period.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.29,0:12:59.28,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.30,0:13:02.71,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're heading back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.51,0:13:09.72,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pigtails.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.18,0:13:14.43,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Kazehaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.43,0:13:15.27,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.14,0:13:33.45,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sadako?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.21,0:13:45.59,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kuronuma Sawako.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.53,0:13:49.35,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.35,0:13:50.85,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.85,0:13:52.23,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your face is so red.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.23,0:13:53.72,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.72,0:13:56.25,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you run that much?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.25,0:13:59.19,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.19,0:14:01.78,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.78,0:14:05.21,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Was there anything special?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.79,0:14:07.61,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't even close to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.61,0:14:11.22,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,He just walked back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.71,0:14:24.59,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I just couldn't stop watching him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.63,0:14:29.83,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All rise.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.98,0:14:32.22,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.22,0:14:33.95,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Done!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.95,0:14:36.10,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go eat, Yano-chin.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.10,0:14:37.82,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You too, Sadako.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.82,0:14:39.25,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about ramen?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.25,0:14:40.37,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.37,0:14:42.52,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to get fat hanging out with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.81,0:14:46.87,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, didn't you need to go shopping?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.87,0:14:51.05,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I need a red t-shirt,\N so that I stand out on sports day.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.05,0:14:52.57,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're coming too, right, Sadako?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.57,0:14:57.77,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to water the plants and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.77,0:14:59.37,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some other time, maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.37,0:15:00.58,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.58,0:15:04.06,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can go shopping after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.06,0:15:05.99,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be faster if we help.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.99,0:15:09.33,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine, not today.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.33,0:15:12.41,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I might...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.94,0:15:16.66,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ask some other time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.39,0:15:18.93,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, we'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.93,0:15:21.38,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shopping too, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.38,0:15:22.81,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.81,0:15:28.89,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Knowing them, they'd probably help me with practice too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.89,0:15:34.19,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll ask you when you're not busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.19,0:15:35.51,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.42,0:15:39.00,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing later, Kazehaya?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.38,0:15:42.42,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Kazehaya-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.93,0:15:52.63,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, what am I doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.44,0:16:15.18,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.74,0:16:17.91,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to borrow the soccer ball?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.91,0:16:18.82,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.82,0:16:20.58,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.58,0:16:22.05,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.05,0:16:24.54,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not for personal use.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.54,0:16:26.53,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you make an exception?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.53,0:16:28.34,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll bring it back, I swear.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.34,0:16:30.14,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said no.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.37,0:16:38.57,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,So much for that plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.57,0:16:42.05,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'll have to buy my own ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.05,0:16:44.02,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll use my New Year's gift money.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.02,0:16:49.33,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this good?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.33,0:16:50.67,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.24,0:16:59.49,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,This is where I first talked to Kazehaya-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.02,0:17:30.40,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh, you're a committee member too?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.40,0:17:32.94,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you too?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.94,0:17:33.96,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's make the best of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.89,0:17:37.14,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tough luck, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.14,0:17:38.88,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This seat's empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.88,0:17:40.45,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.28,0:17:45.08,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, thanks for the CD.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.08,0:17:46.11,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.11,0:17:49.27,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's one I want to borrow off of you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.27,0:17:51.23,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, I'll bring it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.99,0:17:53.03,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.13,0:17:58.29,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That album I lent you before the last one—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.45,0:18:04.31,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you listening, Kazehaya?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.82,0:18:06.65,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My bad, what were you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.65,0:18:09.72,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That CD before the one I lent you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.72,0:18:12.01,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'll bring it next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.37,0:18:38.90,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where the heck are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.16,0:19:07.87,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh, what time is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.77,0:19:49.27,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This way.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.80,0:20:03.35,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.92,0:20:08.31,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't really smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.98,0:20:23.45,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Something's different about the wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.42,0:20:40.94,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,So reach him,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.77,0:20:53.87,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,in place of my smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.77,0:22:26.97,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.72,0:22:30.05,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why does my heart ache?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.13,0:22:34.11,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode: New Friends
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.11,0:22:36.11,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
